1096
00:56:00,789 --> 00:56:03,757
<i>no matter how
off the cuff or casual.</i>

1097
00:56:04,425 --> 00:56:07,019
Now, initially, on coming
into the White House,

1098
00:56:07,094 --> 00:56:09,927
<i>I insisted on
dismantling the system.</i>

1099
00:56:09,997 --> 00:56:13,296
<i>I hadn't liked
