that first moment,</i>

1104
00:56:23,044 --> 00:56:25,172
<i>and you see it in
the challenger's face.</i>

1105
00:56:25,247 --> 00:56:27,373
<i>It's that moment
that he feels</i>

1106
00:56:27,449 --> 00:56:29,781
<i>the impact from
