1122
00:57:12,894 --> 00:57:14,919
<i>So much for
our "ballsy" opening.</i>

1123
00:57:17,799 --> 00:57:20,893
<i>So when did you
actually decide...</i>

1124
00:57:20,969 --> 00:57:23,904
At what moment did you know
you were going to resign?

1125
00:57:23,972 --> 00:57:25,940
<i>That's good. That's good.</i>

1126
00:57:27,142 --> 00:57:31,238
<i>I remember exactly.
It was July 23.</i>

1127
00:57:31,312 --> 00:57:34,146
After it was clear
the Southern Democrats

1128
00:57:34,216 --> 00:57:35,706
that were still against
impeachment had

1129
00:57:35,785 --> 00:57:38,845
<i>had the screws put on them
