1238
01:02:51,269 --> 01:02:54,295
<i>David, we have some
fundamental problems in
our approach that I think...</i>

1239
01:02:54,372 --> 01:02:55,771
<i>Don't worry, Bob.
I'm on it.</i>

1240
01:02:55,841 --> 01:02:56,865
<i>We can use some of
the Kissinger stuff.</i>

1241
01:02:56,942 --> 01:02:58,671
<i>Yeah, but we need
to discuss it sooner
rather than later...</i>

1242
01:02:58,744 --> 01:03:00,109
<i>Look,
I'm disappointed, too.</i>

1243
01:03:00,178 --> 01:03:02,909
But I wonder,
